answer:
Change this:

for all sprites:
{
    graphicsDevice.SetRenderTarget(D);
    &lt;draw sprite i&gt;

    graphicsDevice.SetRenderTarget(P);
    &lt;Draw D&gt;
}


to this:

for all sprites:
{
